data.description:
Beautiful well cared for home. Boasts a very private courtyard surrounded by lush landscaping! Home is light and bright inside with very nice Plantation Shutters, Home has Breakfast Room, Bar and Formal Dining areas. Split floorplan with a den that has attached shelving.
Master bedroom has Bay Windows, Master Bath has private privy and safety bar in shower plus walk-in closet and double sinks. Spare bath has safety bar in tub/shower combo, plus large closet next to it. Ceiling Fans T/O, Entry Hall includes a huge coat closet, and the Utility room has large storage cabinets, Garage has Storage cabinets on two walls. The outside watering system's valves have been recently replaced. Home is surrounded by gorgeous foliage which includes Grapefruit, Orange and the most prolific Lemon Tree!
